p: The effect is close to the one observed for H5N3 and for H7N1 with slight differences in NI 50 values for 1 N for K-525, 1S for K-192, 2 N for K-522 and 2S for K-522 (Fig. 2d). The most active extracts were for strains K-340 grown in 2S condition, K-362 in 2 N and 1Sconditions against H7N1 neuraminidase activity.
